---
Source:
  - Title: Treasury of Traditional Wisdom
    Page: 101
By: Hermes
Tags:
  - Sacrifice-Death=Illusion=The Phantom Flux of Life
  - Life-Love=Faith=Belief in the Unseen
---
That which is dissoluble is destructible; only that which is indissoluble is
everlasting. ...  Nothing that is corporeal is real; only that which is
incorporeal is devoid of illusion.
